Package: ctree
Version: 0.01.1
Date: 2019-9-28
Title: ctree - Clone Tree
Type: Package
Author: Giulio Caravagna
Maintainer: Giulio Caravagna <gcaravagn@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides the implementation of clone trees that can be used to study 
  Cancer Evolution dynamics from bulk sequencing. This package provides several functions to
  generate clone trees from the results of subclonal deconvolution analyses, to plot and summarise
  trees.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
